name: Codemem
tagline: Purpose of this project is to learn certain programming skills like memory managment , multi threading, etc
body:
### Welcome to CodeMem

CodeMem's purpose is to implement a memory management system in a multi-threaded enviroment via c++. The reason
for this is to learn/improve necessary coding-skills. The whole thing right now is a one man show but if you feel like 
you want to contribute to it or just want to do your own thing feel free to fork the project or to push updates to CodeMem.

It is up to you!


### Authors and Contributors
Initiator of the project is (@johanneslueke) Johannes LÃ¼ke
